s with other people?',0,'2017-11-07','2017-02-21 14:33:48'),(5885,11,2,5,'122',1,'During the past 2 years, I have been one of the key figures in establishing a business project, a club, or an association.',0,'2017-11-07','2017-02-21 14:33:48'),(5886,11,2,5,'123',1,'Have you ever attempted something which you did not carry out successfully?',0,'2017-11-07','2017-02-21 14:33:48'),(5887,11,2,5,'124',1,'Are you spontaneous rather than strategic in your thinking?',0,'2017-11-07','2017-02-21 14:33:48'),(5888,11,2,5,'125',1,'Do you easily get impatient?',0,'2017-11-07','2017-02-21 14:33:48'),(5889,11,2,5,'126',1,'When I am working, I often become so engaged that I can forget where I leave my things.',0,'2017-11-07','2017-02-21 14:33:48'),(5890,11,2,5,'127',1,'I tend to \"dig into\" things and go in depth with what I do.',0,'2017-11-07','2017-02-21 14:33:48'),(5891,11,2,5,'128',1,'Do you generally work according to predetermined plans?',0,'2017-11-07','2017-02-21 14:33:48'),(5892,11,2,5,'129',1,'It is typical of me that on some days the desire to get things going simply is not there.',0,'2017-11-07','2017-02-21 14:33:48'),(5893,11,2,5,'130',1,'Are you so balanced that you always remain calm no matter what happens?',0,'2017-11-07','2017-02-21 14:33:48'),(5894,11,2,5,'131',1,'Do you take the time to ponder and reflect on things during the workday, rather than just go ahead all of the time?',0,'2017-11-07','2017-02-21 14:33:48'),(5895,11,2,5,'132',1,'It is typical of me to avoid things and experiences that may prove to be risky, as opposed to those who face risks gladly.',0,'2017-11-07','2017-02-21 14:33:48'),(5896,11,2,5,'133',1,'Do you have so much energy in your body that you often find it difficult to relax and take it easy?',0,'2017-11-07','2017-02-21 14:33:48'),(5897,11,2,5,'134',1,'Is it important for you to have several assignments running simultaneously?',0,'2017-11-07','2017-02-21 14:33:48'),(5898,11,2,5,'135',1,'Have you at any time been in charge of conducting nego