king in the background while you are working?',0,'2017-11-07','2017-02-21 14:33:48'),(5911,11,2,5,'148',1,'Are you usually so resolute to accomplish a certain thing that you are willing to cross the line to reach the goal?',0,'2017-11-07','2017-02-21 14:33:48'),(5912,11,2,5,'149',1,'I am willing to stake everything if I estimate that there is a fair chance of a good reward.',0,'2017-11-07','2017-02-21 14:33:48'),(5913,11,2,5,'150',1,'Are you the one who even during lunch may find it difficult to take it easy, since you are often involved with one thing or another?',0,'2017-11-07','2017-02-21 14:33:48'),(5914,11,2,5,'151',1,'I may find it difficult to wait until someone else has finished speaking, when I feel that I want to say something.',0,'2017-11-07','2017-02-21 14:33:48'),(5915,11,2,5,'152',1,'It is unwise simply to forgive those who have insulted you.',0,'2017-11-07','2017-02-21 14:33:48'),(5916,11,2,5,'153',1,'Even if things do not go my way, I am the persistent type who keeps on going at all costs without wanting to give up.',0,'2017-11-07','2017-02-21 14:33:48'),(5917,11,2,5,'154',1,'Are you so involved in your work and career that you only devote a minimum of your time to family and friends?',0,'2017-11-07','2017-02-21 14:33:48'),(5918,11,2,5,'155',1,'Do you have visions of the future that are usually so great that other people find them difficult to grasp?',0,'2017-11-07','2017-02-21 14:33:48'),(5919,11,2,5,'156',1,'In my current job or in a previous position, I have been responsible for a budget of over Euro 1,000,000.',0,'2017-11-07','2017-02-21 14:33:48'),(5920,11,2,5,'157',1,'Are you one of those who think that one should always completely trust others?',0,'2017-11-07','2017-02-21 14:33:48'),(5921,11,2,5,'158',1,'I usually live in the moment and seldom make up plans longer than 14 days ahead.',0,'2017-11-07','2017-02-21 14:33:48'),(5922,11,2,5,'159',1,'As opposed to being one of the unaffected types, I am more the kind of person who finds it easy to lose heart for some time.',0,'2017-11-07','2017-02-21 14:33:48'),(5923,11,2,5,'160',1,'Does it usually happen that you show your displeasure or irritation for others?',0,'2017-11-07','2017-02-21 14:33:48'),(5924,11,2,5,'161',1,'Are you normally unaffected when you receive bad news about something in which you are involved?',0,'2017-11-07','2017-02-21 14:33:48'),(5925,11,2,5,'162',1,'Are you sometimes in doubt that what you intend to do will work out well?',0,'2017-11-07','2017-02-21 14:33:48'),(5926,11,2,5,'163',1,'Is it more important for you to do things in the most ethical way rather than the way that provides the quickest and the best results?',0,'2017-11-07','2017-02-21 14:33:48'),(5927,11,2,5,'164',1,'I am very careful about always having things well organised around me.',0,'2017-11-07','2017-02-21 14:33:48'),(5928,11,2,5,'165',1,'Do you feel that you get a more realistic perspective by not expecting too much of the future?',0,'2017-11-07','2017-02-21 14:33:48'),(5929,11,2,5,'166',1,'I must restrain myself not to interrupt anyone else in a discussion when I feel I have an excellent argument.',0,'2017-11-07','2017-02-21 14:33:48'),(5930,11,2,5,'167',1,'Are you currently or have you in recent years been the key figure in a project or an activity involving at least 20 other people?',0,'2017-11-07','2017-02-21 14:33:48'),(5931,11,2,5,'168',1,'I often reflect on my own behaviour.',0,'2017-11-07','2017-02-21 14:33:48'),(5932,11,2,5,'169',1,'When I\'m doing something, I can get so absorbed that others must make an effort to get my attention.',0,'2017-11-07','2017-02-21 14:33:48'),(5933,11,2,5,'170',1,'Are you highly competitive in terms of career, job, or business?',0,'2017-11-07','2017-02-21 14:33:48'),(5934,11,2,5,'171',1,'Do you usually avoid being involved in things that are not directly a part of your work?',0,'2017-11-07','2017-02-21 14:33:48'),(5935,11,2,5,'172',1,'To be most efficient, it is best to hand over that part of my job that drags on to those who prefer long-term assignments.',0,'2017-11-07','2017-02-21 14:33:48'),(5936,11,2,5,'173',1,'Are you so quick to start with new assignments that other people may feel that you have once again gone ahead a little too fast?',0,'2017-11-07','2017-02-21 14:33:48'),(5937,11,2,5,'174',1,'When I am dissatisfied with how things relate, I often complain about it, rather than simply keep quiet.',0,'2017-11-07','2017-02-21 14:33:48'),(5938,11,2,5,'175',1,'Could you be happy in a job that does not give you possibilities to develop yourself within your field of business?',0,'2017-11-07','2017-02-21 14:33:48'),(5939,11,2,5,'176',1,'Do you normally keep in the background at conferences, exhibitions or similar events?',0,'2017-11-07','2017-02-21 14:33:48'),(5940,11,2,5,'177',1,'When you receive a new assignment, do you prefer being informed about all the details, rather than just getting the main guidelines?',0,'2017-11-07','2017-02-21 14:33:48'),(5941,11,2,5,'178',1,'I think it is a sensible principle to stay on the safe side and generally avoid taking big risks.',0,'2017-11-07','2017-02-21 14:33:48'),(5942,11,2,5,'179',1,'Do you often surprise other people with your sudden ideas?',0,'2017-11-07','2017-02-21 14:33:48'),(5943,11,2,5,'180',1,'Are you among those who have plans that require extraordinary effort in order to be realized?',0,'2017-11-07','2017-02-21 14:33:48'),(5944,11,2,5,'181',1,'One of my key principles is to consider things carefully to ensure that all aspects are included.',0,'2017-11-07','2017-02-21 14:33:48'),(5945,11,2,5,'182',1,'I prefer that things get done at a calm and controlled pace, rather than a more action-packed form of activities with high pace.',0,'2017-11-07','2017-02-21 14:33:48'),(5946,11,2,5,'183',1,'I belong to those who strive to be better than others, and to be number one in what I do.',0,'2017-11-07','2017-02-21 14:33:48'),(5947,11,2,5,'184',1,'Do you often express what you do not agree with rather than let it be left unsaid?',0,'2017-11-07','2017-0